{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "", "eventName": "", "entryType": "EXTRA", "storyCode": "", "avgTag": "", "storyName": "初稿", "storyInfo": "一篇精雕細琢的稿件終於出爐，劇作家將之交付給了劇團長。\n而就是這樣一張薄薄的紙，將在今後毀滅無數人的生活。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上好的劇本需要用時間來淬煉。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台已寫就，場景已編織。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主角還聽得到劇團的呼喚，主角還會再次登上舞台。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在主角身後，“正義的同伴”羅德島從不缺席。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主角逃離劇團，又在劇團的呼喚下回歸。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懦夫逃離劇團，卻在此刻毅然回首面對我們。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只為搭救一個有著些許關係的......", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陌生人？同伴？好友？", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，他的勇氣已然得證，故事也因此迎來終結。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主角與懦夫都回到了羅德島，回到了他們的家園。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而劇團什麼都沒得到。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報幕人棄離職責，拿起人偶絲線的那一刻——", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他就註定像所有無聊的反派那樣落得個被打倒在地的下場。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顏面盡失。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#11$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不得不說，以這樣的結局收尾是對我個人的褻瀆。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我加了一些段落。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執筆成為阻礙，將創造者的苦難與憤恨強加於主角。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而作為成長的代價，主角將把對創造者的叛逆貫徹到底。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再加上羅德島的介入，我所企盼的，對於角色性格與個人命運的轉變盡皆改道。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由此，故事的終幕就不是我所能著墨的了。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一篇失敗的故事在寫就後便會被焚毀，一切都將從頭來過。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "創作中難免會出些意料之外的差錯，希望您理解。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寫就伏筆，卻發現角色沒有能力前去回收。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鋪墊許久，主角卻倒在了回收伏筆前的那一刻。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不應出現的配角，不應發生的事件，不應面對的障礙。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有不應做出的抉擇。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這確實是我近年來接手的，最具挑戰性的劇本。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#5$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬幸的是，在一次次書寫中，有那麼幾篇熠熠生輝。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而就您的要求來看，我更傾向於推薦您這篇。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艱難險阻被盡掃一空，眾人期盼的美好結局，以及深藏心中的黑暗種子。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當它花開四瓣，結下果實，一切美好終將化為我們所希冀的悲劇。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "命運已成定數，主角茫然無知。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們則在暗處等待，等待著享受結局到來時的無上愉悅。", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_292_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知您意下如何？", "name": "劇作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_292_1#10$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL04", "fadetime": 2.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL04", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.9, "yScaleTo": 0.9, "duration": 40.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長閣下。", "name": "劇作家"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}